What's new in this update:

• New agent: Google Antigravity (the successor to Gemini CLI) is now selectable when you start a conversation — Gemini is retired from the picker.
• Fix: reopening the app mid-reply no longer loses what the agent wrote while you were away — the full response comes back.
• Fix: activity cards no longer cut a sentence in half.
• A smoother animation when you delete a conversation.

Thanks for testing this alpha!
